* Iron Raptor snarled, there was no sign of a message from Liono and she was 
getting impatient.
She looked at the topside guns and saw that they were leaning in the 
opposite direction, this was her chance to act!
Seeing an unguarded air vent she scittered over and removed the grating, she 
took a look back over her shoulder then slipped into the pipe.*

" Stealth Mode!"

* An alternate mode activated and covered her body with a clocking device 
which hid both form and energy signature, it was a little something that she 
had learned back home on Sirose.
Iron Raptor crawled down the pipe and towards a T section in the pipping, 
either way may lead to trouble and in a Predacon ship...trouble was 
enevitable!
This was a perfect opportunity to get to know the enemy and serve Liono all 
at the same time, weather there were enemys' in this ship now are not.*
